dct_alternative_sm: Couleurs-guide-plan aménage Clé Diaphane Offert a sa Clientele par les magasins de la Belle Jardinière Bordeaux
dct_description_sm: Imp. de Vaugrirard, H.-L. Mutti, dir., 12-13, Impasse Ronsin, Paris.
Color legend showing "tramways," "autobus," "tramways suburbains," "bateaux," and "tramways de Bordeaux."
Verso contains roman numerals (in red ink) used for the map key: "Clé Diaphane."
Shows bridge with dotted line "Pont a Transbordeaur," north of the Baside.
Back cover has illustration "Vue de la Succursale de Bordeaux."
